The following system can be virtualised using Vagrant. To start using Vagrant you must have virtual box and vagrant installed on your box:
Oracle VirtualBox - https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads
Vagrant - http://vagrantup.com/

To start the system execute from the source/main/:
	vagrant up

To stop the VM temporarily:
	vagrant halt

To stop the VM completely:
	vagrant destroy

For a list of all other commands:
	vagrant